      "content": "oh i meant a hypothetical scenario or like, the general debate around these kinds of reforms. like if a bill focused on cutting corporate rates and lowering top marginal brackets was passed, what do the different economic models say about how that would hit wealth inequality in the long run? give me a breakdown of the main arguments.",
